<summary>https://psalm.dev/r/6c07857541</summary>

```php
<?php

class A {
	public const A = "foo";
}

$reflected_class = new ReflectionClass(A::class);
foreach ($reflected_class->getReflectionConstants(ReflectionClassConstant::IS_PUBLIC) as $constant) {
    if (is_string($constant->getValue())) {
        echo $constant->getValue();
    }
}
```

